cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.ET, cs.NE 

The paper discusses the use of a quantum annealer for training support vector machines, which is a topic related to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The experiments involve both synthetic and real data, which suggests a focus on data science (cs.DS). The use of a quantum annealer also falls under the category of emerging technologies (cs.ET) and neural networks (cs.NE) due to the potential for quantum computing to improve the performance of machine learning algorithms.
